The paper discusses distributed machine learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses communication and computation in distributed systems, which suggests that it could belong to cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The use of Gaussian processes and online learning suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses convergence on a global model, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses multi-agent systems, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MA (Multiagent Systems).
